{"tid":778647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Razer筆電減料？官方：未說清楚而致歉","createTime":"2018-08-14T00:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T03:40:14.000Z","uid":10717,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"0b507e8b7282590b9edc296611a8ff50483335a7","tid":778647,"uid":10717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/083225_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F083225_70b9ad8557c8b106257128743f423f1d.PNG&h=9e33b2fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRazer Blade 15 2018旗艦筆電標榜是全球最薄的15.6吋電競筆電，主打新的伺服器級散熱部件，筆電價位也相當高，最高規格配置為港幣2萬1499元，換算成台幣約8萬4000元，該型號7月時已在香港開賣，台灣近期將上市，但卻先爆出香港玩家投訴Razer Blade 15筆電偷工減料。<br />\n <br />\n有玩家在購買Razer Blade 15筆電後，因為要升級記憶體，打開機背才發現內部結構和產品網頁宣傳特色不同。原先強調均熱板皆有黑色抗氧化塗層協助散熱，但玩家拿到的筆電並沒此設計，並質疑使用一周均熱板就有氧化的情況出現，令玩家更不滿的是，出現相關問題的用戶在連絡香港代理商及Razer後，並未獲得積極處理，甚至直接更改官網上的產品說明，拿掉「採用黑色外殼，可減少傳導到筆電機身的熱能」這段說明文字，並加註「實品可能與圖片略有差異。」<br />\n <br />\n對於玩家質疑Razer疑似為了趕工在散熱模組偷工減料，台灣Razer則回應：「Razer Blade 15推出後反應熱烈，我們研究方法在提升產量的同時而不影響產品表現。因此，我們在固態硬盤SSD加上導熱墊，取代在均熱片背面塗上石墨塗層。此舉有助提升產量而不影響系統溫度或表現，而兩種設計(均熱片背面塗石墨塗層及SSD加導熱墊)皆能提供同樣效能。」並就未能清楚向消費者交代生產改動而致歉，同時官方也正更新相關的營銷資料。但對於台灣何時上市、均熱片是否也會取消石墨塗層未多加回應。（黃韻文／台北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/083322_36ecc118fc05e1622308da58196c5e37.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F083322_36ecc118fc05e1622308da58196c5e37.PNG&h=7a126168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首批生產的Razer Blade 15(上)，均熱片背面有塗上石墨塗層。而部份用戶拿到的機種(下)，卻改用SSD加導熱墊的方式，取代石墨塗層均熱片。翻攝畫面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/14/083412_6ba8738f06081134a2e5611874011466.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F14%2F083412_6ba8738f06081134a2e5611874011466.PNG&h=5e793a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180813/1410222/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1410222%2F&d=WU70cn3kxO7zAgzGaBbBPf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=6d1a1263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1410222%2F&h=78e9972d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180813/1410222/</a>"},{"pid":"6c18a2c18af0ed86eaacc42a2a27238641bd92c2","tid":778647,"uid":20815,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:38:35.000Z","msg":"Razor: 啲紙皮勁撚過黑色果啲。唔撚識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be5c4fe12905ec13d0ba6aab0b946c64b221bc1","tid":778647,"uid":54787,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:47:06.000Z","msg":"ssd同塊銅係兩part唔同既野黎，講完都唔撚知講乜<br />\n<br />\n答非所問，同香港d議員一9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe92431d9071a3b60b19504aa7b40b1caaab572","tid":778647,"uid":40499,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:50:42.000Z","msg":"呢個牌子 不了"},{"pid":"cc6630e7f8583fad0d099990f1dbb597479ed00e","tid":778647,"uid":21917,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:51:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾razer+香港代理以為改左個官網就唔會違反商品說明條例?(razer blade15事件懶人包)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/buqJsS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/buqJsS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"e7646f415aa666fed027671c4e83f52ed9a5e6c0","tid":778647,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:52:27.000Z","msg":"上連登投訴真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be05626daa02729b979ca7dee4a1ad09e226c441","tid":778647,"uid":6024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:57:46.000Z","msg":"Razer真係廢到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cl